C++17 example of a simple traffic simulation

    Cars move on a 1D road
    Maintain safe distance
    Slow down / speed up
    Console prints road state

Concept (keep it simple but meaningful)
    Road = fixed length (like 50 cells)
    Each car has:
        position
        speed
    Rules:
        accelerate if space ahead
        brake if too close
        move forward every timestep